I"∂ø<p>The organizations are listed roughly in order of when they got involved with blockchain.</p>

<p>I‚Äôm sure to have missed a few things. Please leave an issue, pull request, or contact me if there‚Äôs anything you‚Äôd like included.</p>

<p>Off the top of my head: Bitcoin, Ethereum, Stellar and IOTA have worked w UN. Eventually each may have its own section, as well.</p>

