<h2 id="early-history">Early History</h2>

<ul>
  <li>2010, the UN Commission on Science and Technology for Development [CSTD] proposed the introduction of <a href="http://unctad.org/Sections/wcmu/docs/ecn162010_Israel_en.pdf">a technology-driven universal currency</a>. A ‚ÄúBitMint‚Äù would allow users to transmit funds globally and carry them around on a usb stick.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/BleIVxr.png" alt="" /></p>

